               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">JUDD</hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">and</hi> 
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">HORNER</hi>—<hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <rs id="t18590919-828-verdict-2" type="verdictDescription">
